Packages 
Package Description
eu.acclimatize.unison
Contains the main Unison spring boot application, configuration files, and repositories for storing precipitation and non-precipitation weather data and associated classes.
eu.acclimatize.unison.csvcontroller
Controllers for obtaining data in a CSV format.
eu.acclimatize.unison.harvester
Classes related to periodically obtaining and parsing data from a HARMONIE-AROME API.
eu.acclimatize.unison.jsoncontroller
Controllers that return precipitation and non-precipitation weather data in a JSON format.
eu.acclimatize.unison.location
Contains classes for storing, obtaining, and deleting location data.
eu.acclimatize.unison.location.geodb
Classes for storing coordinates data in a GeoDB database.
eu.acclimatize.unison.location.postgis
Classes for storing coordinates data in a Postgres/PostGIS database.
eu.acclimatize.unison.result
Result row classes that are used by JPQL queries that are specified in ResultQueryConfig.
eu.acclimatize.unison.user
Contains a service that enables tasks be executed that require user credentials and functionality for requesting and storing user information from the console.
